        conda environment helper script
        ===============================
        
        
        .. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/cenv_script.svg
                :target: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/cenv_script
        
        .. image:: https://img.shields.io/travis/technic/cenv_script.svg
